<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Welcome to TRMS</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/styles.css">
    <style>
        body {
            text-align: center;
            background-image: url('/mnt/data/image.png');
            background-size: cover;
            background-position: center;
            color: white;
        }
        .container {
            background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.6);
            padding: 30px;
            margin: 10% auto;
            width: 80%;
            border-radius: 10px;
        }
        .btn {
            background-color: darkgreen;
            color: white;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 5px;
            display: inline-block;
            margin-top: 20px;
        }
        h1, h2 {
            color: white;
            margin: 0;
        }
        p{
            color: white;
        }
        ul{
            list-style-type: none;
            padding: 0;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <h1>Welcome to TRMS</h1>
        <p>TRMS is designed to simplify the booking process for auditoriums and activity rooms in colleges.</p>
        <h2>Features:</h2>
        <ul>
            <li>Easy room booking for users</li>
            <li>Admin control for user management</li>
            <li>View, modify, and cancel bookings</li>
            <li>Secure login system for different user types</li>
        </ul>
        <a href="/login" class="btn">Go to Login Page</a>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
